#~ msgstr "x"

#~ msgid "n"
#~ msgstr "n"

#~ msgid "\\vec{n}"
#~ msgstr "\\vec{n}"

#~ msgid "xy"
#~ msgstr "xy"

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Surface facet (displayed blue) orientation measured as the "
#~ "counterclockwise angle from <inlineequation><mathphrase><placeholder-1/></"
#~ "mathphrase><placeholder-2/></inlineequation>-axis to the projection of "
#~ "facet normal vector <inlineequation><mathphrase><phrase role=\"mathvar"
#~ "\"><placeholder-3/></phrase></mathphrase><placeholder-4/></"
#~ "inlineequation> to <inlineequation><mathphrase><placeholder-5/></"
#~ "mathphrase><placeholder-6/></inlineequation> plane."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Ориентация поверхности грани (показана синим) отсчитываемая как угол "
#~ "против часовой от оси <inlineequation><mathphrase><placeholder-1/></"
#~ "mathphrase><placeholder-2/></inlineequation> до проекции вектора нормали "
#~ "грани <inlineequation><mathphrase><phrase role=\"mathvar\"><placeholder-3/"
#~ "></phrase></mathphrase><placeholder-4/></inlineequation> на плоскость "
#~ "<inlineequation><mathphrase><placeholder-5/></mathphrase><placeholder-6/"
#~ "></inlineequation>."

#~ msgid ""
#~ "Distances and differences can be measured with the <guilabel>Distance</"
#~ "guilabel> tool. It displays the horizontal "
#~ "(<inlineequation><mathphrase>Δ<phrase role=\"mathvar\">x</phrase></"
#~ "mathphrase><alt>\\Delta x</alt></inlineequation>), vertical "
#~ "(<inlineequation><mathphrase>Δ<phrase role=\"mathvar\">y</phrase></"
#~ "mathphrase><alt>\\Delta y</alt></inlineequation>) and total planar "
#~ "(<inlineequation><mathphrase><phrase role=\"mathvar\">R</phrase></"
#~ "mathphrase><alt>R</alt></inlineequation>) distances; the azimuth "
#~ "<inlineequation><mathphrase><phrase role=\"mathvar\">φ</phrase></"
#~ "mathphrase><alt>\\varphi</alt></inlineequation> (measured identically to "
#~ "inclination <inlineequation><mathphrase><phrase role=\"mathvar\">φ</"
#~ "phrase></mathphrase><alt>\\varphi</alt></inlineequation>) and the "
#~ "endpoint value difference (<inlineequation><mathphrase>Δ<phrase role="
#~ "\"mathvar\">z</phrase></mathphrase><alt>\\Delta z</alt></inlineequation>) "
#~ "for a set of lines selected on the data."
#~ msgstr ""
#~ "Расстояния и разницы могут быть измерены с помощью инструмента "
#~ "<guilabel>Расстояние</guilabel>. Он показывает горизонтальные "
#~ "(<inlineequation><mathphrase>Δ<phrase role=\"mathvar\">x</phrase></"
#~ "mathphrase><alt>\\Delta x</alt></inlineequation>), вертикальные "
#~ "(<inlineequation><mathphrase>Δ<phrase role=\"mathvar\">y</phrase></"
#~ "mathphrase><alt>\\Delta y</alt></inlineequation>) и суммарные расстояния "
#~ "на плоскости(<inlineequation><mathphrase><phrase role=\"mathvar\">R</"
#~ "phrase></mathphrase><alt>R</alt></inlineequation>); азимут "
#~ "<inlineequation><mathphrase><phrase role=\"mathvar\">φ</phrase></"
#~ "mathphrase><alt>\\varphi</alt></inlineequation> (измеренный подобно "
#~ "наклону <inlineequation><mathphrase><phrase role=\"mathvar\">φ</phrase></"
#~ "mathphrase><alt>\\varphi</alt></inlineequation>) и разность значений "
#~ "конечных точек(<inlineequation><mathphrase>Δ<phrase role=\"mathvar\">z</"
#~ "phrase></mathphrase><alt>\\Delta z</alt></inlineequation>) для набора "
#~ "выбранных линий."
